title: Superheroes vs. the NFL Combine
description:
Yup, it's Combine time, but we're gonna talk about comic books so deal with it. TOPICS INCLUDE:
- Jared Lorenzen would dust you
- Vernon Davis vs. The Hulk, who ya got
- To this day, all DC characters are written by 8-year-old boys
- Character risk? Captain America’s old tweets are a red flag
- Which Big 12 team is Galactus?
- Advanced analytics: We already know which X-Man would win the 3-cone drill
- We love our big stupid Thor
